{
  "title": "Xtra Roasted Canadian Lentil Casserole",
  "description": "A hearty, post-workout Canadian dish featuring roasted green and red lentils in a crispy, en-croute crust, perfect for a satisfying dinner",
  "cuisine": "Canadian",
  "diet": [
    "macrobiotic",
